Q: 飞机注册号为N790Z的飞机是哪一家公司的？
SQL: SELECT sd.supplier_name FROM aircraft_details ad JOIN supplier_details sd ON ad.supplier_id = sd.supplier_id WHERE ad.registration = "N790Z";
actual_SQL:
SELECT supplier_name
FROM supplier_details
WHERE supplier_id IN
    (SELECT supplier_id
     FROM aircraft_details
     WHERE pure_reg = 'n790z')
LIMIT 50;
